38376>>>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
38379>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38379>>>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38379>>>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38379>>>>>        Handle hoDD
38379>>>>>
38379>>>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38380>>>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38381>>>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38382>>>>>
38382>>>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38382>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38383>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38384>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
38385>>>>>        WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to False
38386>>>>>
38386>>>>>        If (NavigateData.bReadOnly) Begin
38388>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to True
38389>>>>>        End
38389>>>>>>
38389>>>>>        Else Begin
38390>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to True
38391>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to True
38392>>>>>            WebSet pbRender of oDeleteBtn to bHasRecord
38393>>>>>        End
38393>>>>>>
38393>>>>>    End_Procedure
38394>>>>>
38394>>>>>    Procedure OnViewSaved Handle hoServer Boolean bChanged
38397>>>>>        // Close after save
38397>>>>>        Send NavigateClose Self
38398>>>>>    End_Procedure
